thread.title: Redington India to sell iPhone 6s, 6s Plus from Oct 16
thread.title_full: Redington India to sell iPhone 6s, 6s Plus from Oct 16 | Business Standard News

author: Press Trust of India
title: Redington India to sell iPhone 6s, 6s Plus from Oct 16
text:
Apple's iPhone 6s and iPhone 6s Plus will be available in India from October 16 at Redington India, one of the main distributors of iPhones.

The iPhones would be available for purchase across India at its 3,000 retail outlets, Chennai-based Redington India said in a statement.

Apple Inc began the sales of iPhone 6s and iPhone 6s Plus in United States and in other countries recently.

Redington India, which began operations in 1993, currently has its presence in India, the Middle East, Africa, Turkey and Sri Lanka.

Shares of Redington India were trading at Rs 110.30 apiece, down by 0.81 per cent on the BSE.
